reviewText: Arrived on time and happy its part of my collection to watch!
My daughter is a big anime fan and this video came very quickly.
I bought this anime for my Sister's friend Sam, she loved it.

Just got the series in today. I love this series in general and was looking forward to watching it; however, when opening the dvd, it was already scratched up pretty badly and the dvds weren't even on there right. I've noticed a lot about this series, its never in good condition. I still recommend this, but just beware that your dvd might not work.

I think You Did a Wonderful Job in this Product.
I like this Anime.
You Did a Good JOb!
Thank You!
